## Tech Stack

- **Chunking:** `tree-sitter` + `tree-sitter-typescript` (local Node.js)
- **Descriptions:** `@cursor/sdk` `Agent.prompt`, model `composer-2`
- **Embeddings:** Workers AI `@cf/baai/bge-small-en-v1.5` (384-dim, cosine)
- **Vector store:** Cloudflare Vectorize
- **Metadata store:** Cloudflare D1
- **Worker runtime:** Cloudflare Workers (Wrangler)
- **CLI runner:** `tsx`
